ntury, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes was born about 1168, in Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 4 daughters with Hugh Dyve."},"et":{"Abt 1168–":"umbes 1168–Surnud","1164–1210":"1164–1210","1190–Female":"1190–Surnud","1196–Female":"1196–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1168–Female":"1168–Surnud","1190":"1190","14 Feb 1991":"14. veebruar 1991","Abt 1168":"umbes 1168","about 1190":"umbes 1190","1168":"1168","16 Feb 1991":"16. veebruar 1991","1210":"1210","1164":"1164","1196":"1196","about 1196":"umbes 1196","East Haddon, Northamptonshire, England":"East Haddon, Northamptonshire, England","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Dive, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1168–":"noin 1168–Kuollut","1164–1210":"1164–1210","1190–Female":"1190–Kuollut","1196–Female":"1196–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1168–Female":"1168–Kuollut","1190":"1190","14 Feb 1991":"14. helmikuuta 1991","Abt 1168":"noin 1168","about 1190":"noin 1190","1168":"1168","16 Feb 1991":"16. helmikuuta 1991","1210":"1210","1164":"1164","1196":"1196","about 1196":"noin 1196","East Haddon, Northamptonshire, England":"East Haddon, Northamptonshire, England","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Dive, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1168–":"environ 1168–Décédée","1164–1210":"1164–1210","1190–Female":"1190–Décédée","1196–Female":"1196–Décédée","–Female":"Décédée","1168–Female":"1168–Décédée","1190":"1190","14 Feb 1991":"14 février 1991","Abt 1168":"environ 1168","about 1190":"environ 1190","1168":"1168","16 Feb 1991":"16 février 1991","1210":"1210","1164":"1164","1196":"1196","about 1196":"environ 1196","East Haddon, Northamptonshire, England":"East Haddon, Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Dive, Northamptonshire, England":